ou have a question related to undergraduate admissions to the College of Visual Arts and Design, please contact one of our advisors listed below.If you have a question related to graduate admissions to the College of Visual Arts and Design, please contact a graduate advisor in your particular department. If you have a question or problem related to admissions to the university at the undergraduate level, you should contact UNT Undergraduate and Transfer Admissions at 800-868-8211.If you have a question or problem related to admissions to the university at the graduate level, you should contact the Toulouse Graduate School at 940-565-2383. CVAD Student Services Office Office Location: Art Building, Room 111 Office Hours: Monday - Friday 8:00 am - 5:00 pm By appointment onlyPhone: 940-565-2216artadviseasst@unt.edu Advisors for Undergraduate Students Derrick Echoles | Director of Advising (T-Z)Phone: 940-565-2216Email: Derrick.Echoles@unt.eduART 111 Jennifer Grund | Academic Advisor II (A-E)Phone: 940-565-2216Email: Jennifer.Grund@unt.eduArt 111 Laura Hernandez | Academic Advisor II (M-S)Phone: 940-565-2216Email: Laura.Hernandez@unt.eduArt 111 Debbie Shifflett | Academic Counselor (F-L)Phone: 940-565-2216Email: Debbie.Shifflett@unt.eduArt 111 Advisors for Graduate Students Phone: 940-565-3621E-mail: design@unt.eduART 237 Phone: 940-565-7671E-mail: studio@unt.eduART 316 Phone: 940-565-4777E-mail: aeah@unt.eduART 224   Visit UsCollege of Visual Arts & Design 1201 W. Mulberry Denton, TX, 76201 [map] Mail Us College of Visual Arts & Design University of North Texas 1155 Union Circle #305100 Denton, TX, 76203-5017 Contact Us (940) 565-2855 General info: cvad@unt.edu Website issues: artsupport@unt.edu Site last updated on Disclaimer| AA/EOE/ADA| Privacy| Electronic Accessibility| State of Texas Online| Emergency Preparedness| THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information| UNT Compliance Hotline| Governors Committee on People with Disabilities| Texas Veterans Portal